thread.title: Ogden Town Justice

author: democratandchronicle.com
title: Ogden Town Justice
text:
Name: Michael P. Schiano. Address: 269 Ogden Center Road Spencerport.
Occupation: Attorney and Judge.
Salary and term of elected position: $32,760/Four-year term.
Party lines: Republican, Conservative and Independence.
How long incumbent has served: 16 years.
Top priority if elected: To continue serving the community with integrity, honor and dignity.
